That, as we read it in, I guess, our Western modern sort of mindset, seems to be quite simply saying to you, if you persistently keep on doing the things that you know to be wrong,

07:58.594 --> 08:07.287
then you kind of run out of the grace of salvation, and there is only judgment therefore awaiting you.

08:07.307 --> 08:19.225
Now, while I believe there are maybe passages in the Bible that you could more easily get that idea from, I don't think this is one of them.

08:19.605 --> 08:21.047
